#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
", and feel free\n"
"                        to"
msgstr ""
", ແລະ ສາມາດ\n"
"                        ໄປຫາ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. Go to the \"Sales\" App and create a new quotation using the main \"New\""
" button on the top left."
msgstr ""
"1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ \"ການຂາຍ\" ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ \"ໃໝ່\" ຢູ່ທາງເທິງເບື້ອງຊ້າຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Go to the Barcode App, and select \"Operations\"."
msgstr "1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ ບາໂຄດ, ແລະ ເລືອກ \"ການດຳເນີນການ\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Go to the Purchase App."
msgstr "1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ ການຈັດຊື້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Point of sale"
msgstr "1. ຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. View results"
msgstr "1. ເບິ່ງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. We can now go through your weekly replenishment report to ensure a good "
"supply in your shop. To do so, navigate to the Inventory App &gt; Operations"
" &gt; Replenishment."
msgstr ""
"1. ດຽວນີ້ພວກເຮົາສາມາດກວດເບິ່ງລາຍງານການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າປະຈຳອາທິດຂອງທ່ານ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າມີສິນຄ້າພຽງພໍໃນຮ້"
"ານ. ເພື່ອເຮັດສິ່ງນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ &gt; ການດຳເນີນການ &gt; ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. Welcome Elise, your favorite customer, she wants to buy the \"Da Vinci "
"Code\"."
msgstr ""
"1. ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ Elise, ລູກຄ້າຄົນໂປດຂອງທ່ານ, ລາວຕ້ອງການຊື້ປຶ້ມ \"Da Vinci Code\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. You welcome now Hanna Liseuse, but she has a very specific need. She's "
"looking for \"Media Burn: Ant Farm and the Making of an Image\". You don't "
"have this book in stock, let's order it."
msgstr ""
"1. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານຕ້ອນຮັບ Hanna Liseuse, ແຕ່ລາວມີຄວາມຕ້ອງການທີ່ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງຫຼາຍ. ລາວກຳລັງຊອກຫາ"
"ປຶ້ມ \"Media Burn: Ant Farm and the Making of an Image\". ທ່ານບໍ່ມີປຶ້ມຫົວນີ້ໃນສາງ, ມາສັ່ງ"
"ຊື້ມັນກັນເລີຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. By clicking on the search bar, you can select the \"Weekly "
"replenishment\" filter. It displays every products sold this week and their "
"remaining quantity."
msgstr ""
"2. ໂດຍການຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຕົວຕອງ \"ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າປະຈຳອາທິດ\". ມັນຈະສະແດງທຸກສິນ"
"ຄ້າທີ່ຂາຍໃນອາທິດນີ້ ແລະ ຈຳນວນທີ່ເຫຼືອຢູ່."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Control your stock"
msgstr "2. ຄວບຄຸມສາງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Create a new request for quotation, and start adding your products."
msgstr "2. ສ້າງການຮ້ອງຂໍໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່, ແລະ ເລີ່ມເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Customer orders"
msgstr "2. ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງລູກຄ້າ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Elise also wants to buy a 50€ Gift Card for a friend."
msgstr "2. Elise ຍັງຕ້ອງການຊື້ບັດຂອງຂວັນມູນຄ່າ 50€ ໃຫ້ໝູ່."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. In \"Receipts\", create a new reception by clicking the \"New\" button."
msgstr "2. ໃນ \"ການຮັບສິນຄ້າ\", ສ້າງການຮັບໃໝ່ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໃໝ່\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. Once you've found it on your local books database, go to the sales app and create a new product using its ISBN code : 9781941753354. Define the current distributor in your region by going to the \"Purchase\" tab (use \"My Book\n"
"                Distributor\" for this case)."
msgstr ""
"2. ເມື່ອທ່ານພົບມັນໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນປຶ້ມທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຂາຍ ແລະ ສ້າງສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ລະຫັດ "
"ISBN: 9781941753354. ກຳນົດຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍໃນພາກພື້ນຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໄປທີ່ແຖບ \"ການຈັດຊື້\" (ໃຊ້ \"My "
"Book Distributor\" ສຳລັບກໍລະນີນີ້)."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. They want to get an offer for three copies of \"Harry Potter and the "
"Philosophers Stone,\" \"Hidden Life of Trees,\" and \"Sapiens: Brief History"
" of Humankind.\""
msgstr ""
"2. ເຂົາເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການໃບສະເໜີລາຄາສຳລັບປຶ້ມ \"Harry Potter and the Philosophers Stone,\" "
"\"Hidden Life of Trees,\" ແລະ \"Sapiens: Brief History of Humankind\" ຢ່າງລະສາ"
"ມຫົວ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Choose how much of each you want to buy by entering the value in the \"To"
" Order\" column."
msgstr "3. ເລືອກຈຳນວນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຊື້ໂດຍການປ້ອນຄ່າໃນຖັນ \"ສັ່ງຊື້\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Elise has a customer account; select her using the \"Customer\" button."
msgstr "3. Elise ມີບັນຊີລູກຄ້າແລ້ວ; ເລືອກລາວໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ \"ລູກຄ້າ\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Institutional customers"
msgstr "3. ລູກຄ້າອົງກອນ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Once your quotation is ready, you can email it or confirm it."
msgstr ""
"3. ເມື່ອໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງທາງອີເມວ ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນມັນໄດ້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Scan your products. If it does not exist in your database, they will be "
"created with the correct picture, title, and price."
msgstr ""
"3. ສະແກນສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ. ຖ້າມັນບໍ່ມີໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ພວກມັນຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນພ້ອມກັບຮູບພາບ, ຊື່ເລື່ອງ, ແລະ ລາຄາ"
"ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Set the quantity in negative value to create a reverted purchase."
msgstr "3. ຕັ້ງຄ່າຈຳນວນເປັນຄ່າລົບເພື່ອສ້າງການຄືນສິນຄ້າທີ່ຊື້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. You can now create a new quotation. Type her name in the \"Customer\" "
"field to create a new contact."
msgstr ""
"3. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໄດ້. ພິມຊື່ຂອງລາວໃນຫ້ອງ \"ລູກຄ້າ\" ເພື່ອສ້າງຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ໃໝ່."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Add the product to your quotation by searching for its ISBN. You can "
"directly click on the confirm button to turn your quotation in a Sales "
"Order."
msgstr ""
"4. ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າໃສ່ໃນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານໂດຍການຄົ້ນຫາ ISBN ຂອງມັນ. ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມຢືນຢັນໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ"
"ເພື່ອປ່ຽນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນຄຳສັ່ງຂາຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Check the smart buttons, a new delivery has been created, but you need to"
" have all products in stock."
msgstr ""
"4. ກວດເບິ່ງປຸ່ມອັດສະລິຍະ, ການຈັດສົ່ງໃໝ່ໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນແລ້ວ, ແຕ່ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີສິນຄ້າທຸກຢ່າງໃນສາງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Click then on the \"Order\" button to add it to your purchase orders."
msgstr "4. ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກທີ່ປຸ່ມ \"ສັ່ງຊື້\" ເພື່ອເພີ່ມມັນເຂົ້າໃນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Enter the cost of each new product so you can easily reorder it "
"afterward."
msgstr ""
"4. ປ້ອນຕົ້ນທຶນຂອງແຕ່ລະສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໄດ້ງ່າຍໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Register Elise's payment. You can now go back to your main dashboard by "
"selecting \"Backend\" in the top-right burger menu."
msgstr ""
"4. ລົງທະບຽນການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງ Elise. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດກັບຄືນໄປຫາໜ້າຫຼັກໂດຍການເລືອກ "
"\"Backend\" ໃນເມນູມຸມຂວາເທິງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Weekly replenishment"
msgstr "4. ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າປະຈຳອາທິດ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model:loyalty.reward,description:bookstore.loyalty_reward_2
#: model:product.template,name:bookstore.product_product_17_product_template
msgid "5% on your order"
msgstr "ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ 5% ໃນຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "5. Encode new release"
msgstr "5. ລົງທະບຽນປຶ້ມອອກໃໝ່"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Go to the Inventory App. A new Replenishment is suggested under "
"Operations &gt; Replenishment."
msgstr ""
"5. ໄປທີ່ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ. ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ຈະຖືກແນະນຳພາຍໃຕ້ ການດຳເນີນການ &gt; ການຕື່ມສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Navigate to the Purchase App. You can see that all purchase orders have "
"been created and are ready to be sent to your distributors. Enter your "
"purchase orders and send them to your vendors using the Send by Email "
"button."
msgstr ""
"5. ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຈັດຊື້. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທັງໝົດໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ ແລະ ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະສົ່ງໃຫ້ຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ. "
"ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ສົງໃຫ້ຜູ້ຂາຍໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ ສົ່ງທາງອີເມວ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Validate the reception, and this is it! (A purchase order will be "
"automatically created so you can easily reconcile your vendor bills)."
msgstr ""
"5. ກວດສອບການຮັບສິນຄ້າ, ແລະ ນີ້ແມ່ນຮຽບຮ້ອຍ! (ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດກ"
"ວດສອບກັບໃບບິນຜູ້ຂາຍໄດ້ງ່າຍ)."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"6. If you select your product and click on \"Order\", a new Purchase Order "
"is created, you can then email it to your distributor and confirm the order "
"placement."
msgstr ""
